奸有啲突破 好似之前危城 殺破狼2咁<br />\n場面我覺得非常有誠意 唔止係場重頭戲 有啲車撞人 人跌落街個啲都做得好逼真<br />\n不過兄弟情對比上一套掃毒真係差好遠<br />\n唔知點解睇睇下 覺得三哥個角色都幾岩劉青雲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"屌，嚦咕嚦咕新年財劉華同古仔啲兄弟情重好過呢套嘢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩我兩個仔有一個生性<br />\n好彩你努力讀書出人頭地阿媽先有大屋住咋<br />\n阿媽真係好擔心你阿哥，不務正業，成日掛住打牌<br />\n唔知而家揸兜定瞓天橋底呢"},{"pid":"b0b81746073aa59189f6921d3f41c75c89078dd1","tid":1322694,"uid":172677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5f8ef6ef586868a00becacfa4a92445f046aa73f","tid":1322694,"uid":243529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"第一次入戲院睇邱禮濤，果然唔係普通嘅膠<br />\n<br />\n不過邱生應該好識撈，拍咁 多戲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"佢拍戲出名準時唔超支"},{"pid":"06442bf7686df04b2ce37dc4ab1d2d2a496f873c","tid":1322694,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0b81746073aa59189f6921d3f41c75c89078dd1","tid":1322694,"uid":172677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5f8ef6ef586868a00becacfa4a92445f046aa73f","tid":1322694,"uid":243529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"第一次入戲院睇邱禮濤，果然唔係普通嘅膠<br />\n<br />\n不過邱生應該好識撈，拍咁 多戲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"佢拍戲出名準時唔超支"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/1030-EbolaSyndrome.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F10%2F1030-EbolaSyndrome.jpg&h=9830777d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11b3525c69ec3577814437be7a21fe7292d0b46f","tid":1322694,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔再支持唔係拍比香港人睇的港產片喇 係咁多"},{"pid":"5ce1e4ba15a3ba57d0ff03b56ebe2a41b83bd6a8","tid":1322694,"uid":42879,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTim